hopobject.body: I'm a trainee covis pharma This hard-to-wear trend might take a while to catch on, and Lady Gaga is obviously taking it to the extreme with her high necked, long sleeved version. For a more wearable option, try a pair of leather dungarees. They will achieve the same edgy vibe without the sweaty side effects. We love this faux leather pair from Urban Outfitters, team with a simple white tee for maximum impact.
